MBOMBELA &#8211; Police have warned people who are attending the Mpumalanga Show to please park in the designated areas. Police spokesman Capt Dawie Pretorius said he urged the public to be vigilant about sticking to the designated area, as two vehicles had already been stolen on the first day of the show.&#8220;Both vehicles were parked outside the designated areas so we are warning the public not to do this.&#8221;